text:
This was a nice easy experience.
I found it through JETCOST. co.uk flight search website.
The idea of switching airline off to reduce excess information was a nice feature. Also the companies fighting for your business was good as you see the prices and costs and companies swithich places in terms of offer everytime you adjust your requirements/travel dates..
